<h2>Current post-doctoral fellows and graduate students</h2>

<p>I supervise graduate students at the Université de Québec à
Montreal (UQAM) and co-supervise students at the University of
New Brunswick.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://eric.univ-lyon2.fr/~kaouiche/">Kamel Aouiche</a> is a post-doctoral fellow: data mining and warehousing (with Robert Godin).</li>

