<li>I co-supervise Hazel Webb with <a
href="http://v5o5jotqkgfu3btr91t7w5fhzedjaoaz8igl.unbsj.ca/~kaser/">
Owen Kaser</a> on a Ph.D. in Computer Science in OLAP and Data Mining.</li>
</ul>

